<span key="78b7f321557c40088fbdece3710c4cef"><span offset-key="78b7f321557c40088fbdece3710c4cef:0">Labs manages a set of AWS accounts using the </span></span><a href="https://aws.amazon.com/organizations/" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="705e433aa23246c09e6d0a7a4bf48277" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-33159_259-33160-237__"><span data-key="670cae342334439797c6fbfc29fe8af5"><span data-offset-key="670cae342334439797c6fbfc29fe8af5:0">AWS Organizations</span></span></span></a><span key="3d25bbf4996744aab49148825b11676c"><span offset-key="3d25bbf4996744aab49148825b11676c:0"> service. This allows us to create a structure and better manage dozens of separate accounts.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="b00f3964cf6040b3911b9f34406a99e7"><span offset-key="b00f3964cf6040b3911b9f34406a99e7:0">All student </span></span><a href="../../../../lambda-labs/index.html" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="6b407ad36171454a8f9592cdb09a6dab" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-33159_259-33160-237__"><span data-key="1181b404e1a04a8cafb9d463757ec7e3"><span data-offset-key="1181b404e1a04a8cafb9d463757ec7e3:0">AWS Product Accounts</span></span></span></a><span key="df2e4a772c2749a29d72b240c4f0401a"><span offset-key="df2e4a772c2749a29d72b240c4f0401a:0"> are located in the </span>`Students`<span offset-key="df2e4a772c2749a29d72b240c4f0401a:2"> Organizational Unit (OU).</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="75b9bc65ab6541389e8a044220dcaf65"><span offset-key="75b9bc65ab6541389e8a044220dcaf65:0">Only Engineering Managers can create new AWS Product Accounts.</span></span>

    <span key="277806893fb0460384a4a7fbeb06c5f6"><span offset-key="277806893fb0460384a4a7fbeb06c5f6:0">Labs projects must never use AWS Accounts not managed by Lambda School Labs.</span></span>

<span key="d125e0615c9543abb883c90188fb4ef3"><span offset-key="d125e0615c9543abb883c90188fb4ef3:0">You can see a list of accounts </span></span><a href="https://airtable.com/shrQHnZkU56jOLZe1/tbliohq0z8d3PQj4g" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="6ec8b6032c9b4d0698784097eb7ec034" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-33159_259-33160-237__"><span data-key="6c30c4a9c5334083869c4cd04c1deb35"><span data-offset-key="6c30c4a9c5334083869c4cd04c1deb35:0">here</span></span></span></a><span key="3c9e15689c9948dab18efb4b842875a4"><span offset-key="3c9e15689c9948dab18efb4b842875a4:0">. Note, this list is not automatically updated, if you don't see your account, contact your engineering manager! Thanks.</span></span>

# 

<span key="756ca6775b224828a8b95e9e839c8303"><span offset-key="756ca6775b224828a8b95e9e839c8303:0">IAM Users</span></span>

<span key="79e1972c983848b4a752c8fb07b7d774"><span offset-key="79e1972c983848b4a752c8fb07b7d774:0">Each member of a student team will have an associated IAM User. This IAM User will be created and managed by the APL for the Product.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="3bd37c08b4484e61922c646730e28873"><span offset-key="3bd37c08b4484e61922c646730e28873:0">Only APLs have the ability to provision and manage IAM Users</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="bd8eed5206fb482c9779e2ba3dad5f09"><span offset-key="bd8eed5206fb482c9779e2ba3dad5f09:0">IAM Users have the permissions required to </span></span><a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/IAM/latest/UserGuide/id_credentials_access-keys.html#Using_CreateAccessKey" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="cd8d2f1333314a548415296f39382d2b" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-33159_259-33160-237__"><span data-key="d1798c63c6354ce9a151e5c1d643cb1c"><span data-offset-key="d1798c63c6354ce9a151e5c1d643cb1c:0">create AWS Access keys</span></span></span></a><span key="b261cca457d7472aaa8ec02cce122d1d"><span offset-key="b261cca457d7472aaa8ec02cce122d1d:0"> for their own use</span></span>

# 

<span key="28f8f80f877944dc83a17f0c33ce8ab1"><span offset-key="28f8f80f877944dc83a17f0c33ce8ab1:0">IAM Groups</span></span>

<span key="9c0a5204407849059155afb09ef3f8de"><span offset-key="9c0a5204407849059155afb09ef3f8de:0">Each account will have a group named </span>`Students`<span offset-key="9c0a5204407849059155afb09ef3f8de:2"> that all student IAM Users will be assigned to. This group has only specific permissions required for their project, adhering to the </span></span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Principle_of_least_privilege" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="320a8afa625c4be2982de281e05b2dcb" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-33159_259-33160-237__"><span data-key="0c120ca8896c463da65ceed04a8d3698"><span data-offset-key="0c120ca8896c463da65ceed04a8d3698:0">Principle of Least Privilege</span></span></span></a><span key="585794e7312049e4afa310176c17e071"><span offset-key="585794e7312049e4afa310176c17e071:0">.</span></span>

# 

<span key="475cf373bfa3441e9794a9a2ecc73392"><span offset-key="475cf373bfa3441e9794a9a2ecc73392:0">Labs Bot</span></span>

<span key="96fc5f4c5bd748858f9c01d609c458a7"><span offset-key="96fc5f4c5bd748858f9c01d609c458a7:0">Labs APLs will have access to a Slack Bot that will allow them to manage user accounts for student teams.</span></span>
